caller_intent: The caller, Gordy Gorgy, is assisting a member of State Employees Credit Union in obtaining auto insurance with State Employees as the first lien holder. He is seeking guidance on the required documentation.
resolution_steps: Agent explains that the declaration page is needed for the insurance request.
Caller is informed that the declaration page can be requested via the support email.
Caller expresses urgency, prompting the agent to offer to transfer the call to the service team.
knowledge_required: Understanding insurance documentation requirements (e.g., declaration pages)
Knowledge of lien holder processes in auto insurance
summary: A caller from State Employees Credit Union seeks assistance with auto insurance documentation for a member, specifically requiring the declaration page. The agent explains the process and offers to transfer the call to the service team for urgent resolution.
